{"type": "article", "id": 34463, "title": "Amercian Apparel 终于卖了，以及，三叶草上海旗舰店更新 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2016-11-15T02:57:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1358, "name": "玩偶"}, {"id": 466, "name": "LVMH"}, {"id": 873, "name": "星巴克"}, {"id": 1331, "name": "雅诗兰黛"}, {"id": 1450, "name": "Star Wars"}, {"id": 3592, "name": "The North Face"}, {"id": 3865, "name": "adidas Originals"}, {"id": 8634, "name": "Supreme"}, {"id": 13655, "name": "Manolo Blahnik"}, {"id": 26358, "name": "A Bathing Ape"}, {"id": 34866, "name": "Amercian Apparel"}, {"id": 34867, "name": "Too Faced"}, {"id": 976, "name": "Rihanna"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161115101004UXSvTbLIgDC06fwE.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/beauty-features/estee-lauder-to-acquire-too-faced-beauty-brand-for-1-4b-10705202/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>雅诗兰黛要买美妆品牌 Too Faced</b></a> | 继收购 Becca 之后，雅诗兰黛的首席执行官 Fabrizio Freda 在昨日宣布，要斥资 14.5 亿美元收购美妆品牌 Too Faced。Too Faced 诞生于 1998 年，因为其产品色彩丰富、个性强烈、具有不同的趣味性，在美国相当出名，更是受到好莱坞的女明星们的青睐。<br></p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/retail/neiman-marcus-cfo-sudden-departure-10704822/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>美国奢侈连锁百货 Neiman Marcus 集团 CFO 突然离职</b></a> | 在为 Neiman Marcus 仅仅工作了一年半之后，它的财务总监 Donald T.Grimes 突然离职。 Neiman Marcus 称 Grimes 的离职并非出于对公司运营政策的不同意见，不过，也并未明确指出 Grimes 离职的真正原因。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/american-apparel-turnaround-dubbed-a-failure-bondholders-to-lose-with-second-bankruptcy-10704693/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Amercian Apparel 出售</b></a> | 在二度申请破产保护之后，Amercian Apparel 以 6600 万美元卖给了加拿大运动品牌 Gilden。不过，后者只买了它的 IP，而不包括店铺。AA 创始人并没有说明这些店铺未来会如何处理，但表示他未来打算做快制造生意，在英美开工厂，为 ASOS、Kanye West 等品牌提供本地制造服务。<br></p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/lvmh-reportedly-poised-to-buy-maison-francis-kurkdjian-10704909/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>LVMH 或将收购法国香水品牌 Maison Francis Kurkdjian</b></a> | 创立于 2009 年的法国香水品牌 Maison Francis Kurkdjian，目前已有两家巴黎门店，三家台湾店，一家马来西亚店及一家迪拜店。它在全世界范围的 400 多家零售商贩售，同时拥有 30 多个专柜。据称，Maison Francis Kurkdjian 去年的销售额为 2500 万美元，比起 2014 年大涨了 40%。日前传出 LVMH 要收购 Maison Francis Kurkdjian 的消息，但 LVMH 并未给出官方回应。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>今年圣诞，<a href=\"http://popbee.com/lifestyle/food/starbucks-candles-hk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">星巴克推出了一系列由回收的咖啡渣做成的商品</a>。包括由咖啡渣、橄榄油和椰子油制成的、用星巴克咖啡杯装着的手工皂，咖啡渣蜡烛和杯垫。整个系列采用了全黑色的包装，看上去也很有型。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161115095020KhVCyAQuINl4kM9t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161115095031Idp1alEvSLJY59Xt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016111509503908bqGURPsdy2lS6m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">Rihanna 和 Manolo Blahnik 合作，推出冬靴系列。这个系列名为<a href=\"http://fashionista.com/2016/11/rihanna-manolo-blahnik-savage\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Savage</a>，包括不同颜色的高跟长筒靴和高跟短靴，售价在 895 和 3995 美元之间，将于 11 月 16 日正式发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161115095101POClusQKGyZVbzB1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161115095110XyiPeczb3IvUJLxK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161115095118X1MBIERZLOtQ6zi5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.999200\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161115095118Ji96fgqDudmLC8hA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161115095127HjuebOJ0ainMvdsK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/11/adidas-originals-shanghai-flagship-new-pattern\" rel=\"nofollow\">adidas Originals 更新了它在上海的旗舰店</a>。这次，adidas 请来了 DJ Allan Marshall 担任视觉设计师，从中国古典祥云、东方明珠以及上海的别称“申”汲取灵感，创作出了一系列视觉图案，让位于上海市南京西路的 adidas 旗舰店焕然一新。<span style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</span></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161115095138Xm0VGrzl8AwqsLva.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161115095149QwfAmbeRZPiv0uKc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016111509515721RgdJbGlLaFqwme.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161115095159HKrPmBhIzknjeFJb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161115095159ahuIODCyqJQ652b4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161115095159V2dHJuIbgwv5eZSL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161115095200TZOhK3NzFRrxHcmX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161115095200Y0awxSDroHI1XZng.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161115095206TFmpQzRLDXqYtjud.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/11/bape-medicom-toy-star-wars-figures-r2d2-c3po\" rel=\"nofollow\">A Bathing Ape 与 Star Wars 及玩具厂商 Medicom Toy 再度合作</a>，发布最新联名珍藏版玩偶。该系列玩偶将于 11 月 23 日在 Medicom To、A Bathing Ape 专卖店及网店发售，售价为 96 美元。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161115095258u2VQkm7o0lWa8pO6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161115095305vktoXC5M10UZYbcx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/11/supreme-x-the-north-face-2016-fall-winter-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">The North Face 和 Supreme 的 2016 秋冬合作款完整公开</a>。该系列包括防水靴、羽绒衣、裤子和三个不同的包款，以落叶印花和亮橙色两种色调贯穿其中。将于 11 月 17 日正式发售。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161115100634oeKzH6qNMlE7tSm2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666342\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161115100634fTd7KNtGgvZWl6Dy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666342\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161115100634TayktPJjuZOslo3F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666342\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161115100641O1e0ADxPoSpy3UTY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666342\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161115100650zUWVe9rb3xJ7EYsj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161115100657aqGA8Of7WbLwKxzr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611151007022dCioemJWGzRB0pg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161115100709DvTlgZcP4VhoEaw1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161115100709IUnCEd405F6zHpth.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161115100709QDwxdSAUulP8YvHy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161115100716ily02nk6erqp5tEw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161115100716UMoqaDVPWNCzcvY1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p>"}